ZELNICK--Ernest, Ph.D. 85, Husband of Harriet, father of Mark and wife Andrea, Ellen and husband Alan Kaplan, and Ronald and wife Jacklyn. Devoted grandfather of Dana and Michael Zelnick, and Aaron and Ariella Kaplan. Founder of Professional Hearing Aid, attorney, renowned audiologist, innovator, author, educator, charitable and always a gentleman. He will be missed by his family, friends and patients who cherished his love and knowledge. There will be a grave side service Friday 10:30 a.m. at New Montefiore Cemetery, Pinelawn, NY.
